data.description:
Gorgeous Westin Homes Barcelona Plan with updates galore! Enter into a two story entry with Rotunda and sweeping staircase, leading to the open Living room with wall of windows!  Check out this dream kitchen with granite counters, Stainless Steel Appliances, counters galore and a long island overlooking living area, Master bedroom with coffered ceilings & his/her vanities with Travertine Counters, luxurious Garden tub & separate glass shower w/seat. Head up the sweeping staircase to 3 oversized bedrooms w/large walk in closets, extra room for studying, Gameroom and custom Media Room!
Check out this huge backyard w/covered patio/deck ready for those family gatherings/Bar B Q!
